flower, candy,

1433
01:32:06,565 --> 01:32:07,916
make me feel good.

1434
01:32:08,518 --> 01:32:10,089
So many letter.

1435
01:32:10,182 --> 01:32:12,667
One letter very special
I never forget.

1436
01:32:13,018 --> 01:32:15,307
From Jorgen Asbjornsen.

