01:32:16,892 --> 01:32:19,439
You got a letter from
Jorgen Asbjornsen?

1438
01:32:20,252 --> 01:32:22,330
Dr. Asbjornsen write me

1439
01:32:23,127 --> 01:32:25,502
say he feel so, so bad

1440
01:32:25,620 --> 01:32:27,471
