so bad for people.

1443
01:32:35,777 --> 01:32:38,582
Dr. Asbjornsen letter
make me feel so good.

1444
01:32:39,059 --> 01:32:40,762
I write letter too,

1445
01:32:40,863 --> 01:32:44,082
say now first time
I happy be small.

1446
01:32:47,327 --> 01:32:50,281
He say me make trip
go Norway any day.

1447
01:32:50,984 --> 01:32:52,632
