sleep over all the abuses.

1473
01:36:06,104 --> 01:36:07,846
It's humbling, huh?

1474
01:36:08,760 --> 01:36:12,081
Nature is such
a patient sculptor.

1475
01:36:12,242 --> 01:36:14,242
Grinding a tiny bit

1476
01:36:14,374 --> 01:36:18,359
each day slowly, slowly
for thousands of years to

1477
01:36:18,437 --> 01:36:22,343
