1479
01:36:28,440 --> 01:36:31,534
What a dreadful waste.

1480
01:36:41,145 --> 01:36:42,901
You'll have to excuse Jorgen.

1481
01:36:42,926 --> 01:36:46,246
These past few days has
been especially hard.

1482
01:36:46,795 --> 01:36:49,389
