there we were in Helsinki,
big and small.

1502
01:37:42,702 --> 01:37:47,460
Climatologists, bacteriologists,
demographers, physicists,

1503
01:37:47,522 --> 01:37:49,069
immunologists,

1504
01:37:49,286 --> 01:37:52,497
26 Nobel Prize
winners among us.

