the end will come--

1510
01:38:10,897 --> 01:38:13,413
environmental disaster,

1511
01:38:13,569 --> 01:38:15,116
pandemic disease,

1512
01:38:15,158 --> 01:38:16,529
unbreathable air,

1513
01:38:16,554 --> 01:38:19,151
impotable water,
not enough food,

